Module com.example.platformerplain
Package com.example.platformerplain.model

Class LevelModel

java.lang.Object
com.example.platformerplain.model.LevelModel
public class LevelModel extends Object
Represents the model for a game level.

The LevelModel class is responsible for loading and initialising the game level, which includes platforms, endpoints, money items, and snakes.

It also manages the collection of these elements within the level.
